{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-devis-document-monprojet",
    "name": "monProjet — Devis & document PDF (collection complète)",
    "description": "IMPORT : Importez ce fichier + l’environnement monProjet-local.postman_environment.json, puis sélectionnez l’environnement dans la liste déroulante.\n\n=== Variables environnement (.postman_environment) ===\n- baseUrl, email, password, registerEmail, registerPassword\n\n=== Variables collection ===\n- accessToken → rempli par les Tests après Register ou Authenticate\n- lastDevisId → mis à jour après add-avec-options ou GET /devis/all\n\n=== Flux ===\n1) Authentication → POST register OU POST authenticate\n2) Devis — add-avec-options (Decorator + PDF)\n\nLes routes /devis/** nécessitent Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}.\nPDF sous devis-pdf/ (répertoire de travail au démarrage Spring Boot).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8082" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "", "description": "Rempli auto (Tests) — ne pas supprimer." },
    { "key": "lastDevisId", "value": "1", "description": "Id devis pour GET/PUT/DELETE — mis à jour par les Tests." },
    { "key": "email", "value": "", "description": "Optionnel : définir ici si tu n’importes pas l’environnement." },
    { "key": "password", "value": "", "description": "Idem authenticate." },
    { "key": "registerEmail", "value": "", "description": "Idem register." },
    { "key": "registerPassword", "value": "", "description": "Idem register (min 6 car.)." }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "description": "Routes publiques /api/v1/auth/** — pas de Bearer.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST register (CLIENT)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200 inscription', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('token JWT présent', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(j.token).to.be.a('string').that.is.not.empty;",
                  "});",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.token);",
                  "console.log('Token enregistré. Utiliser registerEmail / registerPassword pour les prochains logins si besoin.');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"prenom\": \"Demo\",\n  \"nom\": \"Postman\",\n  \"email\": \"{{registerEmail}}\",\n  \"motdepasse\": \"{{registerPassword}}\",\n  \"telephone\": \"87654321\",\n  \"adresse\": \"1 rue Test\",\n  \"ville\": \"Tunis\",\n  \"codepostal\": \"1000\",\n  \"datenaissance\": \"1995-06-15\",\n  \"idRole\": { \"idRole\": 3 }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register",
            "description": "Crée un utilisateur CLIENT (idRole 3). Change `registerEmail` si l’email existe déjà.\nRéponse : { token, role }. Le Tests enregistre `accessToken`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "POST authenticate",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Réponse JWT', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(j.token).to.be.a('string').that.is.not.empty;",
                  "});",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.token);",
                  "console.log('accessToken OK');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"motdepasse\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/authenticate",
            "description": "Connexion avec `email` + `password` (variables collection)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "POST logout",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout",
            "description": "Déconnexion (révoque les tokens selon ton LogoutHandler). À appeler après les tests si besoin."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Devis — CRUD",
      "description": "Toutes ces routes nécessitent Bearer {{accessToken}}.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /devis/all",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('tableau JSON', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array'));",
                  "var arr = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (arr.length && arr[arr.length - 1].idDevis) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('lastDevisId', String(arr[arr.length - 1].idDevis));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/all"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /devis/{id}",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 ou erreur métier', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([200, 404]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/{{lastDevisId}}",
            "description": "Utilise la variable lastDevisId (mis à jour après liste ou après add-avec-options)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /devis/add (sans options ni PDF automatique)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var d = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (d.idDevis) pm.collectionVariables.set('lastDevisId', String(d.idDevis));",
                  "    pm.test('Créé', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(201));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"datedevis\": \"2026-05-03\",\n  \"nomdev\": \"Simple\",\n  \"prenomdev\": \"Add\",\n  \"telephonedev\": 11223344,\n  \"villedev\": \"Tunis\",\n  \"produit\": \"Véhicule CRUD\",\n  \"prixbase\": 30000\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/add"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT /devis/update/{id}",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 si id existe', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([200, 500]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"datedevis\": \"2026-05-03\",\n  \"nomdev\": \"Modifié\",\n  \"prenomdev\": \"PUT\",\n  \"telephonedev\": 99887766,\n  \"villedev\": \"Sfax\",\n  \"produit\": \"Produit mis à jour\",\n  \"prixbase\": 30000,\n  \"montantFinal\": 31000\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/update/{{lastDevisId}}",
            "description": "Contrôleur impose l’id via l’URL. Adapte le corps après un GET réel si besoin."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE /devis/delete/{id}",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('204 No Content ou erreur', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([204, 400, 500]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/delete/{{lastDevisId}}",
            "description": "Destructif : vérifie qu’aucune Demande ne référence ce devis, sinon erreur BD possible."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Devis — add-avec-options (Decorator + PDF)",
      "description": "POST /devis/add-avec-options avec query assurance, frais.\nRéponse 201 + montantFinal. Fichier généré : devis-pdf/devis_{id}_{date}.pdf",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "add-avec-options — assurance + frais",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "var d = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('montantFinal > 0', () => pm.expect(d.montantFinal).to.be.above(0));",
                  "pm.test('montantFinal >= prixbase', () => pm.expect(d.montantFinal).to.be.at.least(d.prixbase));",
                  "if (d.idDevis) pm.collectionVariables.set('lastDevisId', String(d.idDevis));",
                  "console.log('PDF attendu : devis-pdf/devis_' + d.idDevis + '_*.pdf');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"datedevis\": \"2026-05-03\",\n  \"nomdev\": \"Dupont\",\n  \"prenomdev\": \"Alice\",\n  \"telephonedev\": 22123456,\n  \"villedev\": \"Sfax\",\n  \"produit\": \"Peugeot 208\",\n  \"prixbase\": 45000\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/add-avec-options?assurance=true&frais=true"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "add-avec-options — assurance seulement",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "var d = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (d.idDevis) pm.collectionVariables.set('lastDevisId', String(d.idDevis));",
                  "pm.expect(d.montantFinal).to.be.at.least(d.prixbase);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"datedevis\": \"2026-05-03\",\n  \"nomdev\": \"Bernard\",\n  \"prenomdev\": \"Leo\",\n  \"telephonedev\": 33445566,\n  \"villedev\": \"Gabès\",\n  \"produit\": \"Citroën C3\",\n  \"prixbase\": 32000\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/add-avec-options?assurance=true&frais=false"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "add-avec-options — frais seulement",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "var d = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (d.idDevis) pm.collectionVariables.set('lastDevisId', String(d.idDevis));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"datedevis\": \"2026-05-03\",\n  \"nomdev\": \"Abbes\",\n  \"prenomdev\": \"Sara\",\n  \"telephonedev\": 44556677,\n  \"villedev\": \"Bizerte\",\n  \"produit\": \"Toyota Yaris\",\n  \"prixbase\": 28000\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/add-avec-options?assurance=false&frais=true"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "add-avec-options — sans options",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "var d = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.expect(d.montantFinal).to.eql(d.prixbase);",
                  "if (d.idDevis) pm.collectionVariables.set('lastDevisId', String(d.idDevis));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"datedevis\": \"2026-05-03\",\n  \"nomdev\": \"Khelil\",\n  \"prenomdev\": \"Omar\",\n  \"telephonedev\": 55667788,\n  \"villedev\": \"Nabeul\",\n  \"produit\": \"Dacia Sandero\",\n  \"prixbase\": 19000\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/add-avec-options",
            "description": "Query absente : assurance=false et frais=false par défaut. montantFinal = prixbase."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "add-avec-options — erreur prixbase ≤ 0",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('erreur précondition', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([400, 500]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"datedevis\": \"2026-05-03\",\n  \"nomdev\": \"X\",\n  \"prenomdev\": \"Y\",\n  \"telephonedev\": 12345678,\n  \"villedev\": \"Z\",\n  \"produit\": \"Invalide\",\n  \"prixbase\": 0\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/devis/add-avec-options?assurance=true&frais=true"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
